*Ostala* im je još samo jedna mala nada. (Only one small hope was left to them.)

*Ostali* su se pitali šta će biti dalje. (They were wondering what will happen next.)

*Ostalima* je ostao samo zaborav. (Only oblivion was left to the others.)

*Ostalo* im je da čekaju. (They had to wait.)

*Ostalima* je bilo potrebno da prežive. (The others had to survive.)